          <heading>Waiver of hearing on computation of tax</heading>
          <content>
            <p>Sec. 12-368. Waiver of hearing on computation of tax.Section12-368is repealed, effective January 1, 1972, and applicable to estates of persons dying on and after that date. All estates of persons dying before January 1, 1972, shall be subject to the succession tax or inheritance tax laws applicable to them prior to January 1, 1972, and such laws are continued in force for that purpose.
